{"tid":1647563,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［行動］［共識已達］10月20日反赤納粹2.0之五區集會！","createTime":"2019-10-11T20:33:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T15:18:35.000Z","uid":4396,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"2d1c30604f1a578c1b0a7de68a5df61568c51796","tid":1647563,"uid":4396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T20:33:44.000Z","msg":"大家可以睇返我之前的po<br />\n<br />\n反赤納粹遊行2.0  推上熱門攞共識！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1643283\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1643283</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n既然今次NBA、暴雪送左咁多核彈俾我地，我地一定要食住個勢，搞多次反赤納粹。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n由於有手足認為大遊行難散，因此我地可以搞五區集會。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但我對集會地點唔太識確定，請各位手足集思廣益後，開始整文宣同宣傳！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果依個post上唔到熱門，我正式宣布連登只係一個圍爐打飛機的地方，大家可以放棄用連登，轉用其他討論區。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">推爆佢呀！個撚個淨係識話嬲，屌你嬲就做實際行動，化悲憤為力量啦！屌你老母閪！</span><br />\n<br />\n以下開放討論五區集會地點！"},{"pid":"7c9f7e85cc956edbd05cb33e1b94c34a0bbab644","tid":1647563,"uid":4396,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T20:38:45.000Z","msg":"點解做唔返6、7月行動水準？<br />\n<br />\n個個淨係鋪啲新聞上嚟、行動post買少見少。<br />\n<br />\n知唔知就算美國國會復會都冇咁快推到法案？？仲想休息到幾時？而且法案通過左又點呀？係咪全部人就唔使再行動呀？自己香港自己只係口號？<br />\n<br />\n勇武手足可以休息合情合理，但點解話你飛後勤都可以休息你老母你連血同汗都唔流一滴同我講你要休息？"},{"pid":"0efa1f3c1a2c0bc1e4af24f0c6ccf3875c2d4074","tid":1647563,"uid":4396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c9f7e85cc956edbd05cb33e1b94c34a0bbab644","tid":1647563,"uid":4396,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T20:38:45.000Z","msg":"點解做唔返6、7月行動水準？<br />\n<br />\n個個淨係鋪啲新聞上嚟、行動post買少見少。<br />\n<br />\n知唔知就算美國國會復會都冇咁快推到法案？？仲想休息到幾時？而且法案通過左又點呀？係咪全部人就唔使再行動呀？自己香港自己只係口號？<br />\n<br />\n勇武手足可以休息合情合理，但點解話你飛後勤都可以休息你老母你連血同汗都唔流一滴同我講你要休息？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T20:40:06.000Z","msg":"*和理非"},{"pid":"88c9eec1f8c2a56a97d908545daafd6574c50acb","tid":1647563,"uid":4396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T20:40:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"62de1ea889415f80344e5b7d4638f563835a5e49","tid":1647563,"uid":4396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T20:40:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"754aeea899b29caa2b12b21f03bd871c5ee25b47","tid":1647563,"uid":4396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T20:41:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8160a3fc7b12998cfbe391a17989472c463c19ad","tid":1647563,"uid":4396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T20:42:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a8e4f6aa317c560b9657d2107f45f44989f53d79","tid":1647563,"uid":4396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T20:49:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4e3fa44649ba603fa7964396f11e1c8bea3b091c","tid":1647563,"uid":4396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T20:49:36.000Z","msg":"人呢？個個等運到？"},{"pid":"f4344626dbe6e61ebe61d54758c9b5d2131627f8","tid":1647563,"uid":4396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T20:51:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"75f60efc607792a1092c1bc2c0666b03786067b6","tid":1647563,"uid":208813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T20:53:45.000Z",